We recommended and the Management agreed to require:

a.	The different departments/end-user units of the LGU to change the title of their reports from “Annual Procurement Plan (APP)” to “Project Procurement Management Plan (PPMP)”;

b.	The BAC, through the BAC Secretariat to consolidate the PPMPs of end-user units into one APP;

c.	The BAC, through the BAC Secretariat to prepare annually the LGU’s APP in accordance with the form prescribed in GPPB Resolution No. 20-2015 and review and update the same regularly, at least once every six months or as often as may be required by the HoPE; and

