The LDRRM Council, henceforth, submit a copy of the approved annual LDRRMFIP to OCD and DILG-LGOO.

Management require the contractor to fast track the completion of the projects to avoid possible rescindment of contracts as stipulated in Section 68 of Republic Act (RA) No. 9184;

