The Bids and Awards Committee (BAC) carefully evaluate the prospective bidder’s technical, legal and financial capabilities taking into consideration the history and experience of the Municipality with the contractor relative to project undertakings, so that contracts for infrastructure development projects are awarded only to contractors that are reliable to accomplish the projects on time.

